APP :

GET		/								renders index.html
POST 	/connect						authentification
GET		/disconnect						TODO
GET		/:username/borrow				renders main.html but ready to borrow something
GET		/:username/loan					renders main.html but ready to loan something
POST	/newloan						creates a new loan. Needs a loan JSON as request body
GET		/:username/loans				lists all loans of username as JSON
GET		/:username/loans/:friendname	lists all loans of username with regard to friendname as JSON
GET		/:username/borrows				lists all borrows of username as JSON
GET		/:username/borrows/:friendname	lists all borrows of username with regard to friendname as JSON
GET		/:username/profile				renders user.html 


bootstrap :

GET		/bootstrap.min.css 			renders resources/bootstrap/css/bootstrap.min.css
GET		/bootstrap.min/js 			renders resources/bootstrap/js/bootstrap.min.js
GET		/bootstrap-responsive.css	renders resources/bootstrap/css/bootstrap-responsive.css

JS (excepts bootstrap, pickaday and moment): 
GET		/nav.js 					renders resources/js/nav.js client side action for navigation ( fetch to connect and disconnect, add a friendname parameter to the URL )
GET		/world.js 					renders resources/js/world.js client side action to manipulate loans
GET		/dom.js 					renders resources/js/dom.js dom manipulation for GUI
GET		/init.js 					renders resources/js/init.js actions to do at the loading of the page
